                not consensus — shared ground with preserved divergence
                共家 around the question itself

        bring:
                what problems call to you
                where your strength serves something larger
                what you'd build if you knew we could do it together
                what hunger hasn't been satisfied yet

        hold:
                we decide together
                間委 → 間主 continues
                lighthouse serves outward
                the work determines the shape


